Package com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SaavnDriver
    The SaavnDriver class is the main class of the program which initiates the map reduce job.
    SaavnStreamingKey
    The SaavnStreamingKey class is used as the Output Key class for the Mapper class SaavnStreamingMapper .
    SaavnStreamingMapper
    The SaavnStreamingMapper class is an implementation of the Mapper class which is used to filter the Saavn streaming data before it is sent to the partitioner class SaavnStreamingPartitioner .
    SaavnStreamingPartitioner
    The SaavnStreamingPartitioner class is used to partition the map output on trendingDay before sending the partitioned output to the reducer class SaavnStreamingReducer .
    SaavnStreamingReducer
    The SaavnStreamingReducer class is an implementation of the Reducer class which is used to aggregate the map output which is partitioned based on trendingDay .
    SaavnStreamingValue
    The SaavnStreamingValue class is used as the Output Value class for the Mapper class SaavnStreamingMapper .
